Example of AI bloat (verbose and redundant code):
dart
// Redundant state layer
class MediaPlayerState {
  String currentTrack;
  Duration position;
  bool isPlaying;
  List<String> playlist;
  Map<String, dynamic> playbackOptions; // Often unused
}

// Simplified version:
class MediaPlayerState {
  final String currentTrack;
  final Duration position;
  final bool isPlaying;
  final List<String> playlist;
}

The redundant `playbackOptions` layer was eliminated because it mirrored existing state and was not actively used, reducing cognitive load without losing functionality.
